structure.unit: SALES OF REALTY OF PERSONS UNDER DISABILITY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 87, sec. 10, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 350, effective January 2, 1978. -- Transferred 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 1, effective July 1, 1953 from Act of 1882. -- Chapter 14, title 10, Code of Practice, amended 1882 Ky. Acts ch. 991, sec. 1; and ch. 1400, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Procedure for obtaining court approval for sale or mortgage of land in trust subject to life estate -- Disposition of proceeds -- Duties of life tenant.
